":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T15:54:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有point有策略過獨派</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n毛魔雖然係仆街黎 有樣野講得岩就係槍桿子出政權<br />\n冇槍冇武力有咩用"},{"pid":"21cd0562b1de4e9fadf93df2ef983fb3fb665235","tid":470483,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T01:55:13.000Z","msg":"咁偉大既文一定要推俾多d人睇到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7833a0a07c3860ba8ee1b61d1b1bdeaa32c1a782","tid":470483,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T01:58:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲有point有策略過獨派</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n毛魔雖然係仆街黎 有樣野講得岩就係槍桿子出政權<br />\n冇槍冇武力有咩用</blockquote><br />\n陶傑成日話古今得曹操同毛澤東兩個文人搞政治搞得出色"},{"pid":"4bc299b401da12610c83c67bb716ef71aadb3c76","tid":470483,"uid":32588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T02:03:43.000Z","msg":"對毛澤東說，權力大於一切<br />\n為了奪權，就要籠絡人心<br />\n一旦得到了權力，就要不惜一切代價去鞏固自己的權力"},{"pid":"8320c357cf770e51c0a22a4cfc337147083c41d2","tid":470483,"uid":90704,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T04:26:02.000Z","msg":"次次一拎老毛出黎所有大陸狗都hang 機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}